# VANGUARD PAY — EVALUATION ENVIRONMENT
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Instructions: Copy this file to `.env` before running `start.bat` or `start.sh`.
# Operating without a funded keypair will trigger "Simulation Mode."

# [REQUIRED FOR MAINNET/DEVNET EXECUTION]
# Ed25519 Private Key. Provide a Base58 string.
# Note: If omitted, Vanguard will attempt to read `./vanguard-key.json`.
# If neither exists, an ephemeral wallet will be generated (no live transactions can execute).
SOLANA_PRIVATE_KEY=""

# [OPTIONAL: INFRASTRUCTURE RESILIENCE]
# Vanguard gracefully falls back between nodes if a 429 occurs, but you can 
# inject a primary RPC endpoint here for enhanced latency (e.g. Helius/QuickNode).
RPC_URL="https://api.devnet.solana.com"
